# Cloudflare _redirects file for the SlopStopper site.
#
# Format: <from> <to> <status>
#   200 = rewrite (URL stays the same, content from `to` is served)
#   301 = permanent redirect (browser follows to `to`)
#
# Replaces what worker/index.ts used to do before Phase 0 migration:
# the Worker handled the `/feedback` → `/feedback.html` redirect and
# the `/` → `/index.html` rewrite. Cloudflare's static-asset pipeline
# now does both natively via this file.

/feedback   /feedback.html   301
/           /index.html      200
